location.fullValue: The 1678 2 car Alley Plan, Laurel Woods

data.description: Pride Improved by $15K! BEST BUY IN LAUREL WOODS! Call Broker For More Specials! ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 5.49% for VA & FHA qualified buyers! Spectacular Laurel Woods home with custom touches throughout!  Great price for an almost new home with this much to enjoy.  An all-season covered porch greets all who come to this entertainers floor plan. Great room concept with gas fireplace and views of greenery! The living area flows to a kitchen featuring a large island where food & fun intersect.  Quartz counters, laminate floors, and stainless appliances with nice touches like tile backsplash set the quality standard.  The kitchen flows to the dining area, which opens to a private yard with an oversized patio and fire pit.  Three nice bedrooms upstairs with a primary suite suite featuring large walk-in closet and an awesome soaker tub!  Roll down the private alley to a 2-car garage with driveway parking and extra yard. Central AC, High-efficiency gas furnace, and heat pump H20 heater make things just perfect year-round at an affordable price!  All of this is nestled in Laurel Woods master plan community with 3 parks, nature walk trails along the wetlands, and on the very South edge of the City.  The 5.49% loan is assumable for a Veteran or qualified FHA borrower.  Call the broker for more info.    This one is special!
